  "short_description": "Outdoor AC/DC Power Supply 26V 250W, IP67 enclosure, pole/wall mount compatible",
  "description": "The MikroTik MTP250-26V94-OD is a powerful and durable outdoor AC/DC power supply designed for the MikroTik netPower product line. Delivering a 26V DC output with a total power of 250W, it ensures stable and efficient performance even in demanding network environments. The unit comes in a rugged IP67-rated enclosure, providing strong protection against dust, moisture, and harsh weather conditions. This makes it ideal for outdoor or industrial installations. If your MikroTik access points or other devices are designed to operate within a 12–30V input range, this power supply is a perfect fit. The MTP250-26V94-OD offers dependable power delivery for stable network operation in any condition. It supports wide ambient temperatures from -40°C to +70°C, ensuring long-term reliability. Certified under CE, EAC, and RoHS, this outdoor PSU combines safety, quality, and performance to keep your network powered and protected in all environments.",
  "detailed_description": [
    {
      "heading": "",
      "text": "The MikroTik MTP250-26V94-OD is a powerful and durable outdoor AC/DC power supply designed for the MikroTik netPower product line. Delivering a 26V DC output with a total power of 250W, it ensures stable and efficient performance even in demanding network environments. The unit comes in a rugged IP67-rated enclosure, providing strong protection against dust, moisture, and harsh weather conditions. This makes it ideal for outdoor or industrial installations. If your MikroTik access points or other devices are designed to operate within a 12–30V input range, this power supply is a perfect fit. The MTP250-26V94-OD offers dependable power delivery for stable network operation in any condition. It supports wide ambient temperatures from -40°C to +70°C, ensuring long-term reliability. Certified under CE, EAC, and RoHS, this outdoor PSU combines safety, quality, and performance to keep your network powered and protected in all environments."
    }
